main waheguru agge ihi ardaas karda huna hmesa ki gurdas mann ji nu eni lambi umar jrur deyi ki asi puri life mann saheb de new new songs sunde rhiye.... rooh nu skoon mil janda mann saheb ji nu sunke... ona di awaaj ch ena dam ajj vi ki koi young singer vi ona de nere tere vi ni muqabla karn di tan gal hi door di gal aa.... imandar vi ne bahut ajj tak kise party lyi parchaar krde dekhya kise ne???? jdo hans raj hans ji akaali party ch samil hoye si tan kise reporter ne pushya si ki tuci vi kise party ch jan bare sochde ho??? tan mann saheb ne bda hi khoobsurat jawab ditta ki ik singer sab loka da hunda .. kise ik party da ni.. mere fan sarya parties ch ne akaali hon jn congressi...  main politics ch ni ona kde vi... so gurdass mann ji bare tan treef karn lyi word hi ghat jande ne... waheguru sade mann nu hmesa sade ch ewe hi gaonda nachda tapda rakhna... luv u mann saheb ji
